<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاسْتَفْزِزْ}</span> ... اسْتَخِفَّ، وَاسْتَعْجِلْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِصَوْتِكَ}</span> ... بِدُعَائِكَ إِيَّاهُمْ لِلْمَعَاصِي، وَبِالغِنَاءِ وَالمَزَامِيرِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَجْلِبْ}</span> ... اجْمَعْ، وَصِحْ عَلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِخَيْلِكَ وَرَجِلِكَ}</span> ... بِجُنُودِكَ الرَّاكِبِينَ، وَالرَّاجِلِينَ فِي مَعْصِيَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
